  16 May 2006; Thilo Bangert <bangert@gentoo.org> -pound-1.7.ebuild,
  -pound-1.8.3.ebuild:
  removed first batch of vulnerable versions (bug #118541)

  16 May 2006; Thilo Bangert <bangert@gentoo.org> pound-2.0.5.ebuild:
  added a warning about incompatible configuration files in newer versions

*pound-2.0.5 (16 May 2006)

  16 May 2006; Thilo Bangert <bangert@gentoo.org> +files/pound-2.cfg,
  metadata.xml, +pound-2.0.5.ebuild:
  assumed maintainership - added <longdescription>
  added working configuration for 2.0.x - bumped to 2.0.5

  01 Apr 2006; <nixnut@gentoo.org> pound-2.0.3.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc. Bug #118541

  27 Mar 2006; Fernando J. Pereda <ferdy@gentoo.org> pound-2.0.3.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha wrt security bug #118541. Tested by Thomas Cort
  <tcort@cs.ubishops.ca>.

*pound-2.0.3 (18 Mar 2006)

  18 Mar 2006; <solar@gentoo.org> +pound-2.0.3.ebuild:
